tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE website_traffic ( website_id INT PRIMARY KEY, visitor_id INT, timestamp TIMESTAMP, page_visited VARCHAR(255), event_type VARCHAR(50) )

CREATE TABLE WebsiteVisits (
    visit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    visit_time TIMESTAMP,
    page_visited VARCHAR,
    session_id UUID
)

CREATE TABLE UserBehavior (
    behavior_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    behavior_event VARCHAR,
    event_time TIMESTAMP,
    device_type VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE TrafficSources (
    source_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    source_name VARCHAR,
    source_type VARCHAR,
    source_url VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
    visit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    user_id UUID,
    page_id UUID,
    visit_duration INTERVAL
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    signup_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE pages (
    page_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    page_title TEXT,
    page_category TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE user_actions (
    action_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    action_type TEXT,
    action_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action_details JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE pages (
    page_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    page_name VARCHAR(100),
    page_url VARCHAR(200),
    visits INT,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE events (
    event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    event_name VARCHAR(100),
    page_id UUID REFERENCES pages(page_id),
    session_id UUID REFERENCES sessions(session_id),
    event_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE analytics (
    analytics_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    event_id UUID REFERENCES events(event_id),
    user_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    action_taken VARCHAR(100),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
